    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in showroom condition, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen has been meticulously maintained with a documented VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The suspension geometry is optimized via Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, while the limited-slip differential ensures precise torque vectoring. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep luster with zero rock chips, and the interior bolsters show no signs of wear. A mechanically flawless example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
