      "description": "Presented in showroom-ready condition, this vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or swirl marks, having been kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and taut, retaining that signature 'new car' scent with no signs of wear on the bolsters or controls. Every electronic feature and driver-assist technology functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires and includes both original keys, the owner\u2019s manual, and custom all-weather mats. This is arguably the finest example currently on the market, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from a brand-new model.",
